    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there, car lovers! It truly breaks my heart to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for someone else to experience the absolute joy of driving her. I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. You won't find a single spec out of place; she\u2019s been kept in a climate-controlled garage and polished more times than I can count. If you\u2019re looking for that perfect, 'mint' ride that turns heads every time you pull out of the driveway, you\u2019ve found it. Come by, have a coffee, and see for yourself why I\u2019m so proud of this one!",
      "price": 46500.0,
